38
00:02:30,321 --> 00:02:33,001
I see. It sounds serious.

39
00:02:33,621 --> 00:02:37,021
Do you know where the entrance is and where it leads to?

40
00:02:37,841 --> 00:02:39,321
That is the problem.

41
00:02:39,921 --> 00:02:42,441
We keep many precious treasures in this room.

42
00:02:42,941 --> 00:02:45,541
And I know the tunnel leads to the room we are in.

43
00:02:46,061 --> 00:02:47,261
But that is all I know.

44
00:02:48,241 --> 00:02:50,481
